疫情期间口罩供不应求不少人在朋友圈做起卖口罩的生意↓然而，这其中不少人是浑水摸鱼借疫情大发不义之财微信起诉5名销售假冒口罩违法人员，各索赔100万元3月15日，微信表示，微信团队对5名利用微信销售假冒口罩的违法人员分别提起民事诉讼，要求其公开赔礼道歉并各索赔100万元人民币。
Wee Mouth Mask Mask Supply During the epidemic, many people were selling masks in their communities of friends. However, many of them had sued five people for selling fake masks. The letter said on March 15 that the microphone team had filed separate civil suits against five people who had used micro-letters to sell fake masks.
深圳市南山区人民法院已于2020年3月10日正式受理此系列案件。
The Nanshan People's Court of Shenzhen City officially accepted this series of cases on March 10, 2020.
据透露，微信团队经过对用户投诉线索的研判，发现这些不法分子利用朋友圈发布某知名品牌口罩的仿冒品信息，以线上付款、线下发货的方式开展违法活动。
It was revealed that the micro-letter team through the user complaints clues, found that these illegal users use the circle of friends to publish a well-known brand mask counterfeit information, online payment, offline delivery methods to carry out illegal activities.
经品牌权利人权威鉴定，这5位违法人员销售的口罩均为假冒伪劣商品。
By the authoritative identification of the brand rights holders, the five illegal sales of masks are fake commodities.
微信团队在起诉书指出，被告通过微信销售假冒口罩的恶意行为，严重违反了《腾讯微信软件许可及服务协议》相关条款约定，亦严重损害了原告的商誉，给原告及微信产品带来巨大的损失，亦对社会公共利益及正常的市场经营秩序造成巨大的伤害。
The company said in the indictment that the defendant's malicious act of selling fake masks through micromail seriously violated the terms and conditions of the Tencent Microcredit Software License and Service Agreement. It also seriously damaged the reputation of the plaintiff, caused huge losses to the plaintiff and the micro-credit products, and caused great harm to the public interest and normal market operation order.
此外，微信团队发布的数据显示，从2020年1月至目前，经用户举报，微信共计对3200余个发布违禁品售卖信息的微信帐号进行处罚；对1800余个发布违禁品售卖信息的微信群进行处罚。
From January 2020 to date, according to data released by the Microsofts team, users have reported penalties for more than 3,200 micro-credit accounts for publishing information on the sale of contraband, as well as more than 1,800 micro-credit groups that publish information on the sale of contraband.
延伸阅读产销这类口罩，最高可判无期！此前，根据两高两部联合发布的《关于依法惩治妨害新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情防控违法犯罪的意见》规定，生产不符合保障人体健康的国家标准、行业标准的医用口罩、护目镜等医用器材，或者销售明知是不符合标准的医用器材，足以严重危害人体健康的，以生产、销售不符合标准的医用器材罪定罪处罚，最高可判处无期徒刑，并处没收个人全部财产。
If medical masks and goggles that fail to meet the national and trade standards for the protection of human health are produced or sold, they may be convicted of producing or selling substandard medical equipment, with a maximum penalty of life imprisonment and confiscation of all personal property.
生产、销售其他非医用问题口罩，根据刑法第一百四十条、第二百一十四条的规定，还可能构成生产、销售伪劣产品罪或销售假冒商标的商品罪。
The production and sale of other problem masks for non-medical purposes may also constitute the crime of producing or selling fake or substandard products or of selling goods with counterfeit trademarks, in accordance with the provisions of Articles 140 and 214 of the Criminal Law.
生产伪劣口罩并假冒他人商标对外销售的行为，销售额在五万元以上的，同时触犯以上两个罪名，应择一重罪处罚。
The production of fake and inferior masks and the counterfeiting of trademarks of others for sale abroad shall be punished by a felony alternative if the sales amount exceeds 50,000 yuan and the two offences are committed simultaneously.
近日，国家市场监管总局也对外公布一批“联合双打行动”典型案例，其中在非法制售口罩等防护用品案例中，包括很多通过网络渠道销售假冒伪劣口罩的案件，有的涉案金额甚至高达近千万元。
In recent days, the State Administration of Market Supervision announced a number of typical cases of "joint double action," including many cases involving fake and inferior masks sold through Internet channels, including those involving nearly $10 million in illegal production and sale of respirators.
新华社对此评论称，口罩是抗击疫情的重要物资，一些人制假售假发“疫情财”，置公众生命安全于不顾，于理于法不容↓来源：中国青年报综合新华视点、微信派、中国消费者报、北京头条客户端南方都市报等推荐阅读点击大图|泉州楼祸点击大图|牛蛙、竹鼠、食用蛇……这些野味，还能吃吗？。
Some people make fake sales of "epidemic money" and put the lives of the public into disrepute. China Youth Daily's comprehensive view of China, Weixin School, the China Consumer News, the Beijing Headline Client Southern Metropolis Daily, etc. Click Great Picture & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45;
